   "source": [
    "## 🔍 CASP Interaction Legality Framework\n",
    "\n",
    "### Ontological Constraints Verification\n",
    "1. **Entropy Leak Tolerance**: δ ≤ 1e-6\n",
    "2. **Directional Coherence**: Coherence Index ∈ (0, 1]\n",
    "\n",
    "### Interaction Classification\n",
    "- **Resonant Convergence**: Low entropy leak, positive coherence\n",
    "- **Entropic Conflict**: High entropy leak, negative/zero coherence\n",
    "- **Directional Collapse**: Mixed entropic and coherence states\n",
    "\n",
    "### Transition to Force Emergence\n",
    "If CASP constraints are satisfied, the interaction is promotable to a force emergence tensor.\n",
